北营派出所。工作人员表示，警方已经关注到，案件正在办理当中，具体案件是龙城责任区刑警队在办理。 对此，太原市公安局小店分局龙城责任区刑警队相关人士表示，已经接到这个案子。目前，案件正在全力侦办当中，涉事人员已经被全部抓获，老年人没有生命危险，更具体情况稍后等警方通报。另外，据知情人士消息，视频中涉事6人为4男2女，被打的老人及时送医，眉骨骨折，没有生命危险。太原多名年轻人当街殴打老人，警方：涉事人员已抓，老人暂无生命危险 - 上游新闻·汇聚向上的力量"},"attached_info":"ClUI+tCPkon1xPJeEAMaCDgyMTkxODQzIJmj2pUGMDU44gNAC3IJNTM5NTk1NTk5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"68 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-3bab89eda3f08505e39f58ba1952d584_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1656160440.9242651","card_id":"Q_538949989","target":{"id":538949989,"title":"客观地说，朱一龙主演的电影《人生大事》拍得怎么样？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/538949989","type":"question","created":1655879511,"answer_count":165,"follower_count":233,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,3932,222005,732344],"comment_count":10,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClUI+tCPkon1xPJeEAMaCDgyMDQ4NjQ3INfuypUGMAo46QFADHIJNTM4OTQ5OTg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"68 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f62d80860cc53009ffd5e8b95462d569_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1656160440.9248297","card_id":"Q_539293272","target":{"id":539293272,"title":"如何理解濮存昕在《我在人艺学表演》中说的演员「到了最高的门槛，推最后一扇门的时候要解构自己，要复零」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/539293272","type":"question","created":1656036034,"answer_count":39,"follower_count":129,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5419,17509,174278,178021,2061391],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"什么是真正的表演，什么是来自于人民生活中的表演艺术，在社会的广泛关注下，《我在人